commit.message: disable buttons after click, re-enable after get request
complete rebuild of the DestinationActivity and the GetDistance class, now utilizes concurrency and async tasks to avoid running the get request on the main UI thread.
complete rebuild of the AddVehicleActivity and the GetCarInfo class, now utilizes concurrency and async tasks to avoid running the get request on the main UI thread.
add vibrate function to longPress remove
implement home buttons at the top of the screen
full length of list view is now clickable
add better key and naming system
add docs and squash small bugs
Add no connection case for distance calculation
Fix char too shot bug in inputs
